      "description": "## What's New\n\n### Features\n\n- **Import/Export Rules** - You can now backup and restore your autolink rules via JSON files\n  - Export button downloads all rules as a JSON file\n  - Import button lets you restore rules from a previously exported file\n  - Imported rules are appended to your existing list\n  - Validation ensures only valid rules are imported\n\n### Improvements\n\n- **Removed underline from auto links** - Links now blend more naturally with surrounding text\n\n### Documentation\n\n- Added BRAT installation instructions for beta testers\n- Improved README with better screenshot layout\n\n### Internal\n\n- Fixed lint errors and improved code quality\n",
